menu "BrushlessLamp"

config APP_MATTER_ENABLED
    bool "Enable Matter (commissioning + remote control)"
    default y
    help
      Disable to build a motor-only diagnostic firmware that bypasses
      Matter, WiFi, and BLE. Motor initializes immediately at boot and
      the knob drives it in position mode. Used to A/B test whether
      motor smoothness issues come from Matter/WiFi ISR pressure.

endmenu
